Name: LINK TYPE, GENERAL
Explanation: DESCRIBES THE NATURE OF THE LINK BETWEEN TWO OR MORE NODES IN A NETWORK.

Name: TYPE OF WASTE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF WASTE THAT MAY BE TRANSFERRED AT THE SPECIFIED STATION.

Name: ROAD MOVEMENT TYPE
Explanation: SPECIFIES WHETHER THE MOVE CONTAINED IN THE MESSAGE IS FULLY PLANNED, PRECAUTIONARY OR OTHER .

Name: RADAR WARNING RECEIVER AUDIO TYPE
Explanation: THE RADAR WARNING RECEIVER AUDIO TYPE HEARD DURING ENGAGEMENT.

Name: ENGINE TYPE, ANALYSTS DESCRIPTION
Explanation: PROVIDES IN FREE TEXT THE DESCRIPTION OF AN ENGINE IN INTELLIGENCE TERMS.

Name: MEDIA TYPE OF IDENTIFICATION
Explanation: THE TYPE OF MEDIA USED BY THE AIRCRAFT TO COLLECT, STORE, AND PUBLISH DATA DURING MISSION OPERATIONS.

Name: SURFACE-TO-AIR FIRE TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF ENEMY SURFACE-TO-AIR FIRE FRIENDLY AIRCRAFT ENCOUNTERED DURING FLIGHT OPERATIONS.

Name: GUIDANCE TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF GUIDANCE USED BY EMPLOYED WEAPONS SYSTEMS AGAINST ENGAGED TARGETS.
